ABSTRACT
In one embodiment, one or more computing devices deter-
mine, substantially in real time and locally at a mobile
device, one or more current dynamic operating conditions of
the mobile device related to energy consumption by the
mobile device. The computing devices identify a pre-deter-
mined device state that corresponds to the current dynamic
operating conditions of the mobile device and determine,
based at least in part on the pre-determined device state, an
action for the mobile device to take, the action being related
to energy consumption by the mobile device.
